      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem and looks just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been totally pampered, kept tucked away in a garage, and drives like an absolute dream. Seriously, it\u2019s spotless inside and out! I\u2019m only parting with it because our family is growing, but I know whoever takes this home is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
