    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the deep, lustrous paint remains entirely free of imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the undercarriage is as pristine as the exterior. Inside, the premium leather still retains its original scent and supple texture, with absolutely zero wear on the bolsters, carpets, or touchpoints. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized centers, backed by a comprehensive folder of records. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a specimen that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
